//JIT (Just In Time compiler)
 Converts immediate language to machine language in runtime

| Term    | Meaning             | Use                                          |
| ------- | ------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| **CLR** | Runtime environment | Executes IL code, manages memory, GC         |
| **CLS** | Common rules        | Ensures all .NET languages can work together |
